    'en_US' => 'The manuscripts must include a cover page with the author’s name, institution, email address, academic rank and, if appropriate, research title on which the text was based.<p>The manuscripts must be submitted in a Word document file (doc./ docx), font Times New Roman, 12 points, and 1.5 line-spacing. It must include a title in English and Spanish, an abstract (up to 150 words) and keywords (up to 4).</p><p>The manuscript must follow the APA style.</p><div> </div>',
